      <title>华尔街的经济末日论者认为美国经济即将陷入衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/wall-street-s-dwindling-bear-camp-hangs-onto-its-recession-calls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一小部分华尔街经济学家对 2023 年经济的韧性感到惊讶，他们加倍预计美国家庭和企业在新的一年将遭受痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/wall-street-s-dwindling-bear-camp-hangs-onto-its-recession-calls</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
